Interface Composite

All Superinterfaces:
Adaptable, Documented, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, Marked, Marked, ModelElement, NamedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
CompositeImpl
public interface Composite extends NamedElement, Documented
A representation of the model object 'Composite'. A simple class for building hierarchies of documented entities.

The following features are supported:

  • Id
  • Children
